{"tid":724600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook 確認跟 華為，阿里巴巴等52 間公司分享用戶數據","createTime":"2018-07-01T05:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T03:24:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7d35b0077628509dce5f67cd4d92bdb18a34eb","tid":724600,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:11:45.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n<br />\nFacebook 作為全球最多人使用的社交網絡，它掌握了很多人的生活細節甚至私隱，早前就傳出 Facebook 跟手機生產商和軟件開發商分享用戶的資料。日前 Facebook 在回應美國眾議院能源和商業委員會的查詢時，遞交了一份長達 747 頁有關他們跟其他公司分享資料的交易詳情。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果 Facebook 跟 52 間公司分享用戶的資料，包括阿里巴巴、華為、聯想和 OPPO 等大陸企業，而當中有 38 間企業則已經終止了合作，部份是因為企業已經倒閉或停止了相關業務，例如 HP/Palm 和 Inq，另外有 7 間企業的合約會在今年 7 月完結，1 間則會在今年 10 月完結。Facebook 表示 Apple 和 Amazon 的合作會繼續，而 Tobii 則需要繼續合作，以讓肌萎縮側索硬化症患者能夠用眼睛追蹤技術去使用 Facebook 服務。阿里巴巴、Mozilla 和 Opera 就因為瀏覽器有 Facebook 通知功能而繼續，但跟他們分享的數據並不包括用戶的朋友資料。 <br />\nFacebook 在文件中又提及他們在 2014 年收緊分享管制後，曾經給予 61 個第三方軟件開發商，最長 6 個月時間去改變他們的數據收集習慣，當中包括 Hinge 和 Spotify，另外有 5 個開發商通過 Beta 測試曾經取得部份用戶的朋友資料，但就未有進公開是哪些開發商。"},{"pid":"534da4c82d3519821875587447780881c46d271d","tid":724600,"uid":132587,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"如果要我簡一個21世紀最仆街既人<br />\n我會簡朱克伯格"},{"pid":"1f7be575eceb591407c28381496c4f5a62696da7","tid":724600,"uid":55597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:30:35.000Z","msg":"facebook 一直都賣用戶私隱起家<br />\n而用戶覺得自己私隱唔值錢咪繼續用"},{"pid":"84f7d00ea5e85d6ab8f65a42e2b125f3a3f6b4ec","tid":724600,"uid":33357,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"啲資料俾google用都冇fb咁反感"},{"pid":"bc33bc4f0172f109bfc03a6f9f719f7722505763","tid":724600,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"534da4c82d3519821875587447780881c46d271d","tid":724600,"uid":132587,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"如果要我簡一個21世紀最仆街既人<br />\n我會簡朱克伯格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"睇電影社交網絡啦"},{"pid":"6dee8f0383f8c65f8488419a7c66ce766806ef46","tid":724600,"uid":53498,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"朱西伯格仲痴埋支那度,等陣阿侵做鳩埋你就好笑"},{"pid":"61d86eb0064c82008ef9ac8112e417c212864772","tid":724600,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"賤種又唔貼原文LINK <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/07/01/facebook-confirmed-sharing-user-data-with-52-companies/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2Ffacebook-confirmed-sharing-user-data-with-52-companies%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=xrR4dQ4RiWoF%2FSlsPV03VUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a08c4712\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/07/01/facebook-confirmed-sharing-user-data-with-52-companies/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"0fe92213119ea2ef3684d04a9592e3c605c6b53a","tid":724600,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"534da4c82d3519821875587447780881c46d271d","tid":724600,"uid":132587,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"如果要我簡一個21世紀最仆街既人<br />\n我會簡朱克伯格"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"你傻仔姐"},{"pid":"70d109021ea92364a2ebb88a051738bd0e557218","tid":724600,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:59:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa8f349758ee91edbb784ff212435ee6572c5b9","tid":724600,"uid":68802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"fb已del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219fd24142a730d7ef8b142b4c23e1d5bc8c68a5","tid":